CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 12, 1959, pg. A2 reads: "Summer Vacation Is Over for 370,000 Pupils - First Day - Counting parochial schools, 370,000 pupils were back in school Tuesday... Above, at Vann, Hazel R. Stallings, teaching fifth graders music.... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Hazel R. Stallings seated at piano, teaching music to fifth grade class, in classroom interior of Vann Elementary School
